ar in the weak field for both the collision term,\nwhile Nernst coefficient gets reduced (enhanced) for $L$ ($R$) modes\nconsiderably in the BGK collision term.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 19 Nov 2022 19:21:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-22"}
