decoupling of the pure and logarithmic supertranslations is\nalso given.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 20 Nov 2022 10:33:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Nov 2022 13:48:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-22"}
