e roles of coupled modes in the terahertz THG process\nand the tantalizing possibility of coherent control via such couplings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 20 Nov 2022 11:08:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Dec 2022 01:47:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-13"}
